oads/2024/03/NewDad-and-Rachel-Chinouriri-are-among-the-artists-boycotting-SXSW.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="NewDad 和 Rachel Chinouriri 是抵制的艺术家之一" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/NewDad-and-Rachel-Chinouriri-are-among-the-artists-boycotting-SXSW.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/NewDad-and-Rachel-Chinouriri-are-among-the-artists-boycotting-SXSW-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/NewDad-and-Rachel-Chinouriri-are-among-the-artists-boycotting-SXSW-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/NewDad-and-Rachel-Chinouriri-are-among-the-artists-boycotting-SXSW-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/NewDad-and-Rachel-Chinouriri-are-among-the-artists-boycotting-SXSW-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/NewDad-and-Rachel-Chinouriri-are-among-the-artists-boycotting-SXSW-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/newdad">NewDad</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cardinals">Cardinals</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/enola-gay">Enola Gay</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Rachel-Chinouriri">Rachel Chinouriri</a>成为抵制今年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/sxsw">SXSW</a>音乐节的最新艺术家。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/sxsw-best-new-artists-performances-2023-highlights-radar-3417773">SXSW 2023：我们在奥斯汀音乐节上遇到的最令人兴奋的艺术家</a></strong></li></ul><p>由于该活动与以色列-加沙冲突期间的美国军队和武器公司有关联，这些艺术家与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/kneecap-and-sprints-join-list-of-artists-boycotting-sxsw-2024-3599443">Kneecap、Sprints</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lambrini-girls-join-list-of-artists-boycotting-sxsw-we-cant-affiliate-ourselves-whatsoever-3599122">Lambrini Girls</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/scowl">Scowl</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gel">Gel</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-are-pulling-out-from-sxsw-a-music-festival-should-not-include-war-profiteers-3597005">Okay Shalom 和 Squirrelflower 等</a>乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-are-pulling-out-from-sxsw-a-music-festival-should-not-include-war-profiteers-3597005">一起退出了音乐节的表演</a>。</p><p>一年一度的音乐、文化和艺术展示会于 3 月 12 日至 14 日在德克萨斯州奥斯汀举行。</p><p>在社交媒体上的联合帖子中，红雀队、埃诺拉·盖伊、Gurriers、NewDad 和 Sprints 写道：</p><p> “需要明确的是，我们作为‘来自爱尔兰的音乐’乐队将参加任何官方的 SXSW 演出。我们完全声援巴勒斯坦和其他公开反对并抵制 SXSW 的人。</p><p> “美国军队以及国防承包商/那些发送武器摧毁无辜生命的人对这个节日的赞助是一种令人厌恶和应受谴责的行为。将艺术庆典与巴勒斯坦正在发生的种族灭绝联系起来，这本质上是错误的。”</p><p>他们补充道：“我们将在 13 日星期四晚上 8 点在 Velvet Room 举行的“来自爱尔兰的音乐”展示会上发表联合声明，并在 15 日星期五下午 1 点在 Flamingo Catina 举行的全套爱尔兰早餐展示会上发表联合声明。”</p><p>您可以在这里查看完整的帖子：</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">在 SXSW <a href="https://t.co/ED1JotfyG8">pic.twitter.com/ED1JotfyG8</a></p><p> - NewDad (@NewDad) <a href="https://twitter.com/NewDad/status/1767597506437710277?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 3 月 12 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>在 Instagram 上的另一份声明中，Enola Gay 表示“不可能在美国陆军是‘超级赞助商’的音乐节上表演，这意味着 SX 将成为国防承包商的平台……”您可以在此处阅读他们的完整声明： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4YWtmOut9B/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><di